{\f0\fs20\b Task Detail View\b0\par}
{\f0\fs18
Open any task with \b Enter\b0  or by clicking it. Inside the detail view:\par
\u8226?\tab The \b first line\b0  of the text area is the task title (shown on the card).\par
\u8226?\tab Everything \b below the first line\b0  is private notes visible only in this view.\par
\u8226?\tab Press \b Ctrl+Enter\b0  to save and close.\par
\u8226?\tab Press \b Escape\b0  to save and go back to the list.\par
}
\par

{\f0\fs20\b Tasks Are Grouped by Day\b0\par}
{\f0\fs18
Tasks are automatically grouped under \b Today\b0 , \b Yesterday\b0 , day names, or dates. Completed tasks stay visible inline (just dimmed) so you can see your full day at a glance.\par
}
\par

{\f0\fs20\b Data Storage\b0\par}
{\f0\fs18
Your tasks are stored locally at:\par
{\f1\fs16 %APPDATA%\textbackslash FloaTodo\textbackslash todos.json\par}
No account, no cloud, no tracking.\par
}
\par

{\f0\fs18\cf3 FloaTodo \u8212? Built for focus.\cf0\par}
}

